<question type="multichoice">
<name>
<text> Q1 : base_om_2021_fall_train_02_01 </text>
</name>
<questiontext format="html">
<text><![CDATA[
<p>
<p>Рассмотрим модель без константы <span class="math inline">\(y_i = \beta x_i + u_i\)</span>, оцениваемую с помощью МНК. Вектор остатков обозначим <span class="math inline">\(\hat u\)</span>, а вектор из единичек обозначим <span class="math inline">\(s\)</span>.</p>
<p>Выберите верное утверждение</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>По условию первого порядка остатки перпендикулярны регрессорам.</p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
<defaultgrade>1</defaultgrade>
<shuffleanswers>true</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="-20" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(x \perp u\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="-20" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(\hat y \perp x\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="-20" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(\hat u \perp s\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="-20" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(\hat y \perp u\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="-20" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(\hat x \perp \hat u\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<span class="math inline">\(\hat u \perp x\)</span>
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
</question>


